Recently, during Meet &amp; Code event organized by Media 3.0 and SAP Hybris, I&rsquo;ve gave a talk for university and high-school students about basics of Git. Presentation was titled Git - tips &amp; tricks and was organized at the Silesian Univeristy of Technology in the AEI Department where I was studying a few years ago. Presentation covered quite essential usage of Git, which could be helpful for people who are planning to learn it from the scratch. Nevertheless, in the talk I included a few tips, which could be applied even by more advanced users in their daily work. You can view slides from this presentation below.
